summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 76E, Page 180 of The Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to Rezone certain property in Block 29, Little City Farms, Division No. 5 located on the Southeast corner of S.W. Trenton St. and 25th Ave. S.W., from RS 7200 and BC to RM 800 (C.F. 287603 Petition of Richard E. George, et al).
